<subSubSection id="C33329B604A615F5FFB44D47FB82FBC8" pageId="175" pageNumber="176" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B967A3D04A615F5FFB44D47FB82FBC8" blockId="175.[151,1437,744,1085]" pageId="175" pageNumber="176">
<emphasis id="B95DA62F04A615F5FFB44D47FEE0FC7C" bold="true" box="[151,267,878,904]" pageId="175" pageNumber="176">Remarks.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFB807CC04A615F5FE304D47FE55FC7D" author="Aguayo, C. G. C." box="[275,446,878,905]" pageId="175" pageNumber="176" pagination="107 - 128" refId="ref141408" refString="Aguayo, C. G. C. (1935) Espicilegio de moluscos cubanos. Memorias de la Sociedad Cubana de Historia Natural, 9 (2), 107 - 128." type="journal article" year="1935">Aguayo (1935)</bibRefCitation>
introduced 
<taxonomicName id="4C2901BE04A615F5FD654D47FB80FC7D" authority="Aguayo, 1935" authorityName="Aguayo" authorityYear="1935" box="[582,1131,878,905]" class="Gastropoda" family="Triphoridae" genus="Triphora" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Asparagales" pageId="175" pageNumber="176" phylum="Mollusca" rank="subSpecies" species="triserialis" subSpecies="clenchi">
<emphasis id="B95DA62F04A615F5FD654D47FCF5FC7C" box="[582,798,878,904]" italics="true" pageId="175" pageNumber="176">Triphora triserialis</emphasis>
subsp. 
<emphasis id="B95DA62F04A615F5FC574D47FC2EFC7C" box="[884,965,878,904]" italics="true" pageId="175" pageNumber="176">clenchi</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFB807CC04A615F5FCEF4D47FB80FC7D" author="Aguayo, C. G. C." box="[972,1131,878,905]" pageId="175" pageNumber="176" pagination="107 - 128" refId="ref141408" refString="Aguayo, C. G. C. (1935) Espicilegio de moluscos cubanos. Memorias de la Sociedad Cubana de Historia Natural, 9 (2), 107 - 128." type="journal article" year="1935">Aguayo, 1935</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
as a replacement name for 
<taxonomicName id="4C2901BE04A615F5FFB44DBBFD49FC58" authority="Dall, 1881" authorityName="Dall" authorityYear="1881" box="[151,674,914,941]" class="Gastropoda" family="Triphoridae" genus="Triphora" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Asparagales" pageId="175" pageNumber="176" phylum="Mollusca" rank="variety" species="triserialis" variety="intermedia">
<emphasis id="B95DA62F04A615F5FFB44DBBFE9BFC58" box="[151,368,914,940]" italics="true" pageId="175" pageNumber="176">Triphora triserialis</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="B95DA62F04A615F5FE8B4DBBFDCAFC58" box="[424,545,914,940]" italics="true" pageId="175" pageNumber="176">intermedia</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFB807CC04A615F5FD0A4DBBFD49FC58" author="Dall, W. H." box="[553,674,914,940]" pageId="175" pageNumber="176" pagination="33 - 144" refId="ref147874" refString="Dall, W. H. (1881) Preliminary report on the Mollusca. In: Reports on the results of dredging, under the supervision of Alexander Agassiz, in the Gulf of Mexico, and in the Caribbean Sea, 1877 - 1879, by the united states steamer blake. Bulletin of the Museum of Comparative Zoology, 9 (2), 33 - 144." type="journal article" year="1881">Dall, 1881</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, which is preoccupied in his opinion by 
<taxonomicName id="4C2901BE04A615F5FB4D4DBBFF39FC24" authority="Dall, 1881" authorityName="Dall" authorityYear="1881" class="Gastropoda" family="Triphoridae" genus="Triphora" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Asparagales" pageId="175" pageNumber="176" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="intermedius">
<emphasis id="B95DA62F04A615F5FB4D4DBBFAB6FC58" box="[1134,1373,914,940]" italics="true" pageId="175" pageNumber="176">Triphora intermedius</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFB807CC04A615F5FA464DBBFF39FC24" author="Dall, W. H." pageId="175" pageNumber="176" pagination="33 - 144" refId="ref147874" refString="Dall, W. H. (1881) Preliminary report on the Mollusca. In: Reports on the results of dredging, under the supervision of Alexander Agassiz, in the Gulf of Mexico, and in the Caribbean Sea, 1877 - 1879, by the united states steamer blake. Bulletin of the Museum of Comparative Zoology, 9 (2), 33 - 144." type="journal article" year="1881">Dall, 1881</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<bibRefCitation id="EFB807CC04A615F5FFFD4D9FFE60FC25" author="Aguayo, C. G. C." box="[222,395,950,977]" pageId="175" pageNumber="176" pagination="107 - 128" refId="ref141408" refString="Aguayo, C. G. C. (1935) Espicilegio de moluscos cubanos. Memorias de la Sociedad Cubana de Historia Natural, 9 (2), 107 - 128." type="journal article" year="1935">Aguayo (1935)</bibRefCitation>
mistakenly wrote 
<taxonomicName id="4C2901BE04A615F5FD414D9FFB9DFC24" authority="Dall, 1889" authorityName="Dall" authorityYear="1889" box="[610,1142,950,977]" class="Gastropoda" family="Triphoridae" genus="Triphora" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Asparagales" pageId="175" pageNumber="176" phylum="Mollusca" rank="variety" species="triserialis" variety="intermedia">
<emphasis id="B95DA62F04A615F5FD414D9FFCD7FC24" box="[610,828,950,976]" italics="true" pageId="175" pageNumber="176">Triphora triserialis</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="B95DA62F04A615F5FC5B4D9FFC1AFC24" box="[888,1009,950,976]" italics="true" pageId="175" pageNumber="176">intermedia</emphasis>
Dall, 1889
</taxonomicName>
, where 1889 should have been 1881. However, 
<taxonomicName id="4C2901BE04A615F5FEB34DF3FC77FC00" authority="Dall, 1881" authorityName="Dall" authorityYear="1881" box="[400,924,986,1013]" class="Gastropoda" family="Triphoridae" genus="Triphora" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Asparagales" pageId="175" pageNumber="176" phylum="Mollusca" rank="variety" species="triserialis" variety="intermedia">
<emphasis id="B95DA62F04A615F5FEB34DF3FD82FC00" box="[400,617,986,1012]" italics="true" pageId="175" pageNumber="176">Triphora triserialis</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="B95DA62F04A615F5FD804DF3FCF7FC00" box="[675,796,986,1012]" italics="true" pageId="175" pageNumber="176">intermedia</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFB807CC04A615F5FC064DF3FC77FC00" author="Dall, W. H." box="[805,924,986,1012]" pageId="175" pageNumber="176" pagination="33 - 144" refId="ref147874" refString="Dall, W. H. (1881) Preliminary report on the Mollusca. In: Reports on the results of dredging, under the supervision of Alexander Agassiz, in the Gulf of Mexico, and in the Caribbean Sea, 1877 - 1879, by the united states steamer blake. Bulletin of the Museum of Comparative Zoology, 9 (2), 33 - 144." type="journal article" year="1881">Dall, 1881</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
was simply the recognition of varietal rather than specific status for 
<taxonomicName id="4C2901BE04A615F5FEBF4DD7FCE2FBEC" authority="Dall, 1881" authorityName="Dall" authorityYear="1881" box="[412,777,1022,1048]" class="Gastropoda" family="Triphoridae" genus="Triphora" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Asparagales" pageId="175" pageNumber="176" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="intermedius">
<emphasis id="B95DA62F04A615F5FEBF4DD7FD60FBEC" box="[412,651,1022,1048]" italics="true" pageId="175" pageNumber="176">Triphora intermedius</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFB807CC04A615F5FDB14DD7FCE2FBEC" author="Dall, W. H." box="[658,777,1022,1048]" pageId="175" pageNumber="176" pagination="33 - 144" refId="ref147874" refString="Dall, W. H. (1881) Preliminary report on the Mollusca. In: Reports on the results of dredging, under the supervision of Alexander Agassiz, in the Gulf of Mexico, and in the Caribbean Sea, 1877 - 1879, by the united states steamer blake. Bulletin of the Museum of Comparative Zoology, 9 (2), 33 - 144." type="journal article" year="1881">Dall, 1881</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
and not the introduction of a new name, making Aguayo’s replacement name unnecessary as already stated by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFB807CC04A615F5FDFD4A0BFB8EFBC8" author="Rolan, E. &amp; Fernandez-Garces, R." box="[734,1125,1058,1084]" pageId="175" pageNumber="176" pagination="81 - 170" refId="ref167481" refString="Rolan, E. &amp; Fernandez-Garces, R. (2008) New data on the Caribbean Triphoridae (Gastropoda, Triphoroidea) with the description of 26 new species. Iberus, 26, 81 - 170." type="journal article" year="2008">Rolán &amp; Fernández-Garcés (2008)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
